26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 It is necessary to immediately inform the owner of the revealed Internet web-site about this fact, and to notify him of the need to remove the information prohibited for distribution in the Russian Federation immediately. \par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi709\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4066522 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 \par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid12940191 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 After receiving from the hosting provider a notification of inclusion of the domain name and (or) the Internet web-site page link in the Register, the Internet website owner shall take immediate measures to remove and (or) to limit the access to the  Internet web-site containing information prohibited for distribution in the Russian Federation}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 .\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi709\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4066522 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 \par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid4066522 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid4066522\charrsid15403203 In case the Internet web-site owner fails to fulfill this requirement, the hosting provider must restrict the access to the web-site in question within 24 hours from the receipt of the notification}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid10236770\charrsid15403203 .\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid10236770 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid10236770\charrsid15403203 \par In case the Internet web-site owner fails to fulfill this requirement or to act appropriately, the hosting provider is required to limit an access to this Internet web-site within 24 hours. \par \par In case the hosting provider and (or) the Internet web-site owner fail to take these measures, the network address enabling to identify Internet web-sites containing the information prohibited for distribution in the Russian Federation will be decided to be entered into the Register and to be limited for access by operators.\par \par The decision about entering the domain names, Internet web-site page links and network addresses enabling to identify the Internet web-sites containing the information prohibited for distribution in the Russian Federation can be appealed to a court by the owner of the Internet web-site, the hosting provider or the operator providing an access to the Internet data telecommunications network within three months from the date of taking such decision.\par \par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sa200\sl276\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid15498341 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid15403203\charrsid15403203 The information on the availability of Internet web-site page links, Internet domain names and network addresses in the Unified Register is accessible on a 24-hour basis at the following web address: }{\field\flddirty{\*\fldinst {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid15403203\charrsid15403203  HYPERLINK "http://eais.rkn.gov.ru/en/" }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs26 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs26\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\insrsid15403203\charrsid15403203 {\*\datafield 00d0c9ea79f9